title: Alien Workshop X J Mascis X Fender Guitar Video Contest Winn
description:
Zac Childers is the winner of the Alien Workshop x J Mascis x Fender Guitar video contest!

Alien Workshop would like to thank everyone that put the time and effort into submitting their videos for this contest. Everyone that sent in a video did an amazing job, and selecting a winner was a tough decision. We'll be posting more video entries to the AWS site: http://www.alienworkshop.com/

In the end, Zac's video submission was chosen as the winner. Videos were judged on editing, skateboarding, creativity and overall composition.

Music: "Little Fury Things", Written and performed by Dinosaur Jr
©1987 SST Records

"My skate footage in this spans a decade...friends featured include Erich Bielefeldt, Caleb Ocasio, Jack Beckett, Josh Swyers, Mark Eyestone, Shannon Brown, Matt Mirabile and Kelly O'brien. Song is "Little Fury Things" from the album "You're Living All Over Me" , released by Dinosaur Jr. Dec. 14th, 1987." -- Zac Childers
